The schema describes configuration settings for .tsdrc files. It is an object type. The main properties of the schema are: 'strictSSL' is a boolean that indicates whether strict SSL is enabled; it is optional and defaults to true. 'proxy' is a string that specifies any standard http-proxy supported by the request package; it is optional and must be in uri format. 'token' is a string that represents an OAuth token used to increase GitHub API rate limits; it is optional. No additional properties are allowed at the root level.eği
